      <h2>The Idea</h2>
      <p class="left-align">Our idea was simple. We strived to construct a web application that analyzes an image, and creates a musical piece that matches it. We achieved this goal through the use of countless algorithms that take advantage of inherent traits on a given image. Our front end design inspiration came from a strong desire to create something unconventional and different. Thus, PRISM was created. Now anyone can find their own sound and create what is quite literally the soundtrack of their life.</p>
